  "texts": [
    "To test the intuitive physics capabilities of the different LLMs, we used photographs depicting wooden block towers from ref.",
    "98 (see Supplementary Fig. 1 for an example).",
    "We first asked models to determine the background colour of the image.",
    "All four models achieved almost perfect accuracy (Fig. 2a).",
    "We then asked models to state the colour of blocks from top to bottom."
  ],
